						<span class="bg-black px-3 py-2 text-white">Phi Hung</span>
						<span class="hidden xl:inline">Frontend / Interface / Web3</span>
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="mono mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.34em] text-neutral-600">React / Next.js / TailwindCSS</p>
